{"tid":354513,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"招連登巴絲一齊玩PUBG絕地求生(奉上好用優化一個)","createTime":"2017-08-10T13:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T11:02:23.000Z","uid":111050,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fbb9258707d37656830b1a51f00ecfdd37ef310","tid":354513,"uid":111050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:49:07.000Z","msg":"如題  [HK NO.1]<br />\n我自己就好憎同街場排 因為佢會開咪亂叫又唔聽指示合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無奈玩依隻GAME既朋友唔多 所以想搵人玩 想打搶箱又得 龜縮戰法又得 自己玩可能兩日玩廿場先食一兩次雞<br />\n<br />\nBTW 想加入PUBG既巴絲或者配置唔夠玩既可以試下用依個youtuber既優化<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j-FcQ3rXfWw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj-FcQ3rXfWw&d=ZmXSrbDKmsQzFN1FCt4cqp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=afcd0a80\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j-FcQ3rXfWw</a><br />\n 佢有分兩PART 真心幾好用 至少唔會再跳FPS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n SETUP方法LINK入面有講 依個YOUTUBER有時會出優化教學同小知識  所以我覺得幾好 佢依家個DISCORD好似已經發展到有100個人都係玩PUBG<br />\n<br />\n利申:之前無聊睇佢兩日直播 又入左佢DISCORD玩左一場  not bad~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9876e1592e093a54bfd75ff9cf9b62cdd4bb04e6","tid":354513,"uid":124689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d997a2622ef3d1dae7f835109b92e90a6eaa9719","tid":354513,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"個server係咪收左皮?"},{"pid":"effb831be2a4a59a81028896aecad38841343d91","tid":354513,"uid":51592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba02c143d79cc296f8ac0dbc4e12837b5e783ff","tid":354513,"uid":111050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個server係咪收左皮?</blockquote><b